* VOLTEST.INP using BPTI coordinates
*

stream datadir.def

OPEN READ FORM UNIT 1 NAME @0toph10.rtf
READ RTF  CARD UNIT 1
CLOSE UNIT 1
BOMLEV -2
OPEN READ FORM UNIT 2 NAME @0param8.prm
READ PARAMETER CARD UNIT 2
CLOSE UNIT 2
BOMLEV  0

READ SEQUENCE CARDS
* PTI SEQUENCE
*
   58
ARG PRO ASP PHE CYS LEU GLU PRO PRO TYR 
THR GLY PRO CYS LYS ALA ARG ILE ILE ARG
TYR PHE TYR ASN ALA LYS ALA GLY LEU CYS 
GLN THR PHE VAL TYR GLY GLY CYS ARG ALA
LYS ARG ASN ASN PHE LYS SER ALA GLU ASP 
CYS MET ARG THR CYS GLY GLY ALA
GENERATE  MAIN
PATCH DISU MAIN  5 MAIN 55
PATCH DISU MAIN 14 MAIN 38
PATCH DISU MAIN 30 MAIN 51
READ SEQUENCE WATER 4
GENERATE  SOLV

open unit 3 read card name @0bpti.crd
READ COORD card  UNIT 3
CLOSE UNIT 3

COOR COPY COMP
COOR STAT

!!!!! 1 First marker for VOLTEST
! compute volume
SCALAR WMAIN SET 2.5
COOR SEARCH RCUT  4.0 -
      XMIN -22.0 XMAX 22.0 XGRID 110 -
      YMIN -15.0 YMAX 15.0 YGRID 75 -
      ZMIN -18.0 ZMAX 14.0 ZGRID 80
SCALAR X = WMAIN

!!!!! 2 Second marker for VOLTEST
!
SCALAR WCOMP SET 2.5
SCALAR WCOMP STORE 1
SCALAR WCOMP SET 4.0
SCALAR WCOMP STORE 2
COOR VOLUME COMP SPACE 660000
SCALAR Y = WCOMP

!!!!! 3 Third marker for VOLTEST
!
!COOR VOLUME COMP SPACE 66000
SCALAR WCOMP SET 2.5
COOR SEARCH COMP RCUT  4.0 -
      XMIN -24.0 XMAX 24.0 XGRID 110 -
      YMIN -17.0 YMAX 17.0 YGRID 75 -
      ZMIN -20.0 ZMAX 16.0 ZGRID 80
SCALAR Z = WCOMP

!!!!! 4 Fourth marker for VOLTEST
!
SCALAR WMAIN MULT -1.0
SCALAR WMAIN STORE 3
SCALAR Y +STORE 3
SCALAR WMAIN RECALL 3
PRINT COOR
stop

